  <entry>
    <title>如何用Rust语言构建API</title>
    <url>/2025/08/18/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%94%A8Rust%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BAAPI/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>[toc]</p>
<h1 id="用-Rust-和-Actix-web-从零开始写一个-RESTful-API"><a href="#用-Rust-和-Actix-web-从零开始写一个-RESTful-API" class="headerlink" title="用 Rust 和 Actix-web 从零开始写一个 RESTful API"></a>用 Rust 和 Actix-web 从零开始写一个 RESTful API</h1><blockquote>
<p>目标读者：有 Rust 基础、第一次用 Actix-web 的同学<br>阅读时间：20 分钟<br>最终成果：一个能跑在本地 8080 端口、带 CRUD 的 Todo API，并附带完整的目录结构与测试用例。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="1-为什么要选-Actix-web？"><a href="#1-为什么要选-Actix-web？" class="headerlink" title="1. 为什么要选 Actix-web？"></a>1. 为什么要选 Actix-web？</h2><p>Actix-web 是目前 Rust 生态里<strong>性能最好</strong>、<strong>文档最完整</strong>、<strong>第三方支持最多</strong>的 Web 框架之一。<br>它基于 actor 模型，配合 async&#x2F;await，QPS 实测能轻松破 100k（当然，我们的重点还是“开发体验”）。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="2-环境准备"><a href="#2-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="2. 环境准备"></a>2. 环境准备</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>工具</th>
<th>版本</th>
<th>作用</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>rustc</td>
<td>≥ 1.75</td>
<td>Rust 编译器</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>cargo</td>
<td>随 rustc 自带</td>
<td>包管理</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>PostgreSQL</td>
<td>任意</td>
<td>数据持久化（本文使用 SQLx + Postgres）</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>cargo-watch</td>
<td>可选</td>
<td>热重载</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 Rust（已安装可跳过）</span></span><br><span class="line">curl --proto <span class="string">&#x27;=https&#x27;</span> --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 cargo-watch（开发时自动重启）</span></span><br><span class="line">cargo install cargo-watch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="3-创建项目骨架"><a href="#3-创建项目骨架" class="headerlink" title="3. 创建项目骨架"></a>3. 创建项目骨架</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cargo new actix_todo_api --bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> actix_todo_api</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-1-目录结构（先放“目标图”）"><a href="#3-1-目录结构（先放“目标图”）" class="headerlink" title="3.1 目录结构（先放“目标图”）"></a>3.1 目录结构（先放“目标图”）</h3><p>最终目录长这样：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── Cargo.toml</span><br><span class="line">├── .env               # 存放 DATABASE_URL</span><br><span class="line">├── migrations/        # SQLx migrate</span><br><span class="line">│   └── 20240818120000_init_todos.sql</span><br><span class="line">├── src</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── main.rs</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── config.rs      # 读取 env 变量</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── models.rs      # 实体 + SQLx 映射</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── handlers.rs    // 路由处理函数</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── routes.rs      // 路由注册</span><br><span class="line">│   └── schema.rs      // 请求/响应 DTO</span><br><span class="line">└── tests</span><br><span class="line">    └── api_test.rs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="4-引入依赖"><a href="#4-引入依赖" class="headerlink" title="4. 引入依赖"></a>4. 引入依赖</h2><p>编辑 <code>Cargo.toml</code>，<strong>复制粘贴即可</strong>：</p>
<figure class="highlight toml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[package]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">name</span> = <span class="string">&quot;actix_todo_api&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">version</span> = <span class="string">&quot;0.1.0&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">edition</span> = <span class="string">&quot;2021&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[dependencies]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">actix-web</span> = <span class="string">&quot;4&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tokio</span> = &#123; version = <span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>, features = [<span class="string">&quot;macros&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;rt-multi-thread&quot;</span>] &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">serde</span> = &#123; version = <span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>, features = [<span class="string">&quot;derive&quot;</span>] &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">serde_json</span> = <span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 数据库</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">sqlx</span> = &#123; version = <span class="string">&quot;0.7&quot;</span>, default-features = <span class="literal">false</span>, features = [</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;runtime-tokio-native-tls&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;macros&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;postgres&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;uuid&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;chrono&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">] &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">dotenvy</span> = <span class="string">&quot;0.15&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">uuid</span> = &#123; version = <span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>, features = [<span class="string">&quot;v4&quot;</span>] &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">chrono</span> = &#123; version = <span class="string">&quot;0.4&quot;</span>, default-features = <span class="literal">false</span>, features = [<span class="string">&quot;clock&quot;</span>] &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[dev-dependencies]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">reqwest</span> = <span class="string">&quot;0.11&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="5-创建-Postgres-数据库"><a href="#5-创建-Postgres-数据库" class="headerlink" title="5. 创建 Postgres 数据库"></a>5. 创建 Postgres 数据库</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1) 安装 psql 客户端（略）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2) 建库</span></span><br><span class="line">createdb actix_todo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3) 写 .env</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;DATABASE_URL=postgres://<span class="variable">$USER</span>@localhost/actix_todo&quot;</span> &gt; .<span class="built_in">env</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="6-写第一个-migration"><a href="#6-写第一个-migration" class="headerlink" title="6. 写第一个 migration"></a>6. 写第一个 migration</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 sqlx-cli（一次性）</span></span><br><span class="line">cargo install sqlx-cli --no-default-features --features postgres</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建迁移文件</span></span><br><span class="line">sqlx migrate add init_todos</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑 <code>migrations/xxxxxxxx_init_todos.sql</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE</span> EXTENSION IF <span class="keyword">NOT</span> <span class="keyword">EXISTS</span> &quot;uuid-ossp&quot;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE TABLE</span> todos (</span><br><span class="line">    id          UUID <span class="keyword">PRIMARY KEY</span> <span class="keyword">DEFAULT</span> uuid_generate_v4(),</span><br><span class="line">    title       TEXT <span class="keyword">NOT NULL</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    done        <span class="type">BOOLEAN</span> <span class="keyword">NOT NULL</span> <span class="keyword">DEFAULT</span> <span class="literal">FALSE</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    created_at  TIMESTAMPTZ <span class="keyword">NOT NULL</span> <span class="keyword">DEFAULT</span> NOW(),</span><br><span class="line">    updated_at  TIMESTAMPTZ <span class="keyword">NOT NULL</span> <span class="keyword">DEFAULT</span> NOW()</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>执行迁移：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlx migrate run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="7-编码阶段"><a href="#7-编码阶段" class="headerlink" title="7. 编码阶段"></a>7. 编码阶段</h2><h3 id="7-1-读取配置"><a href="#7-1-读取配置" class="headerlink" title="7.1 读取配置"></a>7.1 读取配置</h3><p><code>src/config.rs</code></p>
<figure class="highlight rust"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> dotenvy::dotenv;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> sqlx::postgres::PgPoolOptions;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> sqlx::&#123;Pool, Postgres&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> std::env;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">pub</span> <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Config</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> database_url: <span class="type">String</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> port: <span class="type">u16</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">impl</span> <span class="title class_">Config</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">from_env</span>() <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">Self</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_ invoke__">dotenv</span>().<span class="title function_ invoke__">ok</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">Self</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            database_url: env::<span class="title function_ invoke__">var</span>(<span class="string">&quot;DATABASE_URL&quot;</span>).<span class="title function_ invoke__">expect</span>(<span class="string">&quot;DATABASE_URL must be set&quot;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">            port: env::<span class="title function_ invoke__">var</span>(<span class="string">&quot;PORT&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                .<span class="title function_ invoke__">unwrap_or_else</span>(|_| <span class="string">&quot;8080&quot;</span>.<span class="title function_ invoke__">to_string</span>())</span><br><span class="line">                .<span class="title function_ invoke__">parse</span>()</span><br><span class="line">                .<span class="title function_ invoke__">expect</span>(<span class="string">&quot;PORT must be a number&quot;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> <span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">db_pool</span>(&amp;<span class="keyword">self</span>) <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> Pool&lt;Postgres&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        PgPoolOptions::<span class="title function_ invoke__">new</span>()</span><br><span class="line">            .<span class="title function_ invoke__">max_connections</span>(<span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            .<span class="title function_ invoke__">connect</span>(&amp;<span class="keyword">self</span>.database_url)</span><br><span class="line">            .<span class="keyword">await</span></span><br><span class="line">            .<span class="title function_ invoke__">expect</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Failed to create pool&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="7-2-定义模型"><a href="#7-2-定义模型" class="headerlink" title="7.2 定义模型"></a>7.2 定义模型</h3><p><code>src/models.rs</code></p>
<figure class="highlight rust"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> chrono::&#123;DateTime, Utc&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> serde::&#123;Deserialize, Serialize&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> sqlx::FromRow;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> uuid::Uuid;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[derive(Debug, Serialize, Deserialize, FromRow)]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">pub</span> <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Todo</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> id: Uuid,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> title: <span class="type">String</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> done: <span class="type">bool</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> created_at: DateTime&lt;Utc&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> updated_at: DateTime&lt;Utc&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[derive(Debug, Deserialize)]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">pub</span> <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">CreateTodo</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> title: <span class="type">String</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[derive(Debug, Deserialize)]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">pub</span> <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">UpdateTodo</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> title: <span class="type">Option</span>&lt;<span class="type">String</span>&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">pub</span> done: <span class="type">Option</span>&lt;<span class="type">bool</span>&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="7-3-路由处理函数"><a href="#7-3-路由处理函数" class="headerlink" title="7.3 路由处理函数"></a>7.3 路由处理函数</h3><p><code>src/handlers.rs</code></p>
<figure class="highlight rust"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> actix_web::&#123;delete, get, post, put, web, HttpResponse, <span class="type">Result</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> sqlx::PgPool;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> uuid::Uuid;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> crate::models::&#123;CreateTodo, Todo, UpdateTodo&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[get(<span class="string">&quot;/todos&quot;</span>)]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">find_all</span>(pool: web::Data&lt;PgPool&gt;) <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> <span class="type">Result</span>&lt;HttpResponse&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">todos</span> = sqlx::query_as::&lt;_, Todo&gt;(<span class="string">&quot;SELECT * FROM todos ORDER BY created_at DESC&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        .<span class="title function_ invoke__">fetch_all</span>(pool.<span class="title function_ invoke__">get_ref</span>())</span><br><span class="line">        .<span class="keyword">await</span></span><br><span class="line">        .<span class="title function_ invoke__">map_err</span>(|_| actix_web::error::<span class="title function_ invoke__">ErrorInternalServerError</span>(<span class="string">&quot;DB error&quot;</span>))?;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_ invoke__">Ok</span>(HttpResponse::<span class="title function_ invoke__">Ok</span>().<span class="title function_ invoke__">json</span>(todos))</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[post(<span class="string">&quot;/todos&quot;</span>)]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">create</span>(</span><br><span class="line">    pool: web::Data&lt;PgPool&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">    form: web::Json&lt;CreateTodo&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">) <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> <span class="type">Result</span>&lt;HttpResponse&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">rec</span> = sqlx::query_as::&lt;_, Todo&gt;(</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">r#&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        INSERT INTO todos (title) VALUES ($1)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        RETURNING *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;#</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="title function_ invoke__">bind</span>(&amp;form.title)</span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="title function_ invoke__">fetch_one</span>(pool.<span class="title function_ invoke__">get_ref</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="keyword">await</span></span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="title function_ invoke__">map_err</span>(|_| actix_web::error::<span class="title function_ invoke__">ErrorInternalServerError</span>(<span class="string">&quot;DB error&quot;</span>))?;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_ invoke__">Ok</span>(HttpResponse::<span class="title function_ invoke__">Created</span>().<span class="title function_ invoke__">json</span>(rec))</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[get(<span class="string">&quot;/todos/&#123;id&#125;&quot;</span>)]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">find_one</span>(<