<h1 id="Actix-web-超精简版逐行注解"><a href="#Actix-web-超精简版逐行注解" class="headerlink" title="Actix-web 超精简版逐行注解"></a>Actix-web 超精简版逐行注解</h1><p>下面把刚才 20 行代码重新贴一遍，<strong>每行都加注释</strong>，并说明“<strong>为什么要这么做</strong>”。</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="1-Cargo-toml"><a href="#1-Cargo-toml" class="headerlink" title="1. Cargo.toml"></a>1. <code>Cargo.toml</code></h3><figure class="highlight toml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[dependencies]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">actix-web</span> = <span class="string">&quot;4&quot;</span>          <span class="comment"># 引入 Actix-web 框架核心</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tokio</span> = &#123; version = <span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>, features = [<span class="string">&quot;macros&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;rt-multi-thread&quot;</span>] &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># tokio 是 Rust 异步运行时；Actix-web 基于它。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># features：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#   macros —— 允许 #[tokio::main] 宏</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#   rt-multi-thread —— 多线程调度器，提升并发性能</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="2-src-main-rs"><a href="#2-src-main-rs" class="headerlink" title="2. src/main.rs"></a>2. <code>src/main.rs</code></h3><figure class="highlight rust"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 引入需要的类型和宏</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">use</span> actix_web::&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    get, post,           <span class="comment">// 属性宏：把函数标记为 GET/POST 处理器</span></span><br><span class="line">    web,                 <span class="comment">// 提取器（extractor）：从 HTTP 请求中取数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    App, HttpResponse,   <span class="comment">// App：路由表；HttpResponse：构建响应</span></span><br><span class="line">    HttpServer, Responder <span class="comment">// HttpServer：监听 TCP；Responder：任何可转成 HTTP 响应的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 定义 GET &quot;/&quot; 处理器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[get(<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>)]</span>              <span class="comment">// 宏：自动注册路由 GET /</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">index</span>() <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">impl</span> <span class="title class_">Responder</span> &#123; <span class="comment">// impl Responder：返回任何实现 Responder 的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Hello, Actix!&quot;</span>      <span class="comment">// &amp;&#x27;static str 已自动实现 Responder，直接返回文本</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 定义 POST &quot;/echo&quot; 处理器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[post(<span class="string">&quot;/echo&quot;</span>)]</span>         <span class="comment">// 宏：自动注册路由 POST /echo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">echo</span>(</span><br><span class="line">    body: web::Json&lt;serde_json::Value&gt; <span class="comment">// web::Json&lt;T&gt; 提取器</span></span><br><span class="line">                                       <span class="comment">// 把请求 JSON 自动反序列化成 serde_json::Value</span></span><br><span class="line">) <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">impl</span> <span class="title class_">Responder</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    HttpResponse::<span class="title function_ invoke__">Ok</span>().<span class="title function_ invoke__">json</span>(body.<span class="title function_ invoke__">into_inner</span>()) <span class="comment">// 把收到的 JSON 原样返回</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// HttpResponse::Ok() 生成 200 状态码</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// .json(...) 把任意可序列化类型变成 JSON 响应</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// body.into_inner()：取出内部的 serde_json::Value</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 入口函数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#[actix_web::main]</span>       <span class="comment">// 宏：把 main 变成 async 并启动 tokio 运行时</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">fn</span> <span class="title function_">main</span>() <span class="punctuation">-&gt;</span> std::io::<span class="type">Result</span>&lt;()&gt; &#123; <span class="comment">// io::Result&lt;()&gt; 用于处理 bind/run 时的错误</span></span><br><span class="line">    HttpServer::<span class="title function_ invoke__">new</span>(||   <span class="comment">// 新建服务器，闭包里返回 App 实例</span></span><br><span class="line">        App::<span class="title function_ invoke__">new</span>()       <span class="comment">// 新建路由表</span></span><br><span class="line">            .<span class="title function_ invoke__">service</span>(index) <span class="comment">// 注册 index 处理器</span></span><br><span class="line">            .<span class="title function_ invoke__">service</span>(echo)  <span class="comment">// 注册 echo 处理器</span></span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="title function_ invoke__">bind</span>((<span class="string">&quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</span>, <span class="number">8080</span>))? <span class="comment">// 绑定地址端口；? 传播错误</span></span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="title function_ invoke__">run</span>()                    <span class="comment">// 启动异步服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">    .<span class="keyword">await</span>                     <span class="comment">// 等待服务器结束（Ctrl-C）</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="3-运行命令"><a href="#3-运行命令" class="headerlink" title="3. 运行命令"></a>3. 运行命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cargo run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><code>cargo run</code> 编译 + 执行</li>
<li>第一次会下载依赖并编译；后续增量编译只要几秒。</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id="4-测试请求"><a href="#4-测试请求" class="headerlink" title="4. 测试请求"></a>4. 测试请求</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -X POST localhost:8080/echo \</span><br><span class="line">     -H <span class="string">&#x27;Content-Type: application/json&#x27;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">     -d <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&quot;msg&quot;:&quot;hi&quot;&#125;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><code>-X POST</code> 指定 HTTP 方法</li>
<li><code>-H</code> 设置请求头，告诉服务器发送的是 JSON</li>
<li><code>-d</code> 指定请求体</li>
<li>服务器收到后原样返回，验证链路正常。</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id="总结一句话"><a href="#总结一句话" class="headerlink" title="总结一句话"></a>总结一句话</h3><p><strong>每行代码都是最小必要步骤</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>框架依赖 → 路由宏 → 处理器 → 服务器启动 → 运行测试。</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
